GenomeCutter version 0.01
==============================

INSTALLATION
This is a stand alone perl script used for estimating fragment size distribution of single/double enzyme cutting.

COPYRIGHT AND LICENCE

Copyright (C) 2016 by Yongbin Zhuang (happye321@gmail.com)

This  is free software; you can redistribute it and/or modify
it under the same terms as Perl itself, either Perl version 5.18.2 or,
at your option, any later version of Perl 5 you may have available.

Notice:
If you have miniconda installed, make sure,in your $PATH variable, /usr/bin/perl is before   the dir of minicoda/bin/

METHODOLOGY
EnzymeI recognization site: AATT
EnzymeII recognization site: GATC
Example:
Radseq:
              I1       I2                I3                         I4                         I5       I6      
        cccccAATTcccccAATTcccccGATCcccccAATTcccccGATCcccccGATCcccccAATTcccccGATCcccccGATCcccccAATTcccccAATTcccccGATC
             ----     ----              ----                       ----                       ----     ----          
 AATT:  ------  -------  ----------------  -------------------------  -------------------------  -------  ----------
          L1       L2            L3                    L4                         L5                 L6        L7
  # of Enzyme cutting site: 6
  Average length= sum(L1..L7)/7
  
ddRADseq
              I1       I2      II1      I3       II2      II3      I4       II4      II5      I5        I6      II6
        cccccAATTcccccAATTcccccGATCcccccAATTcccccGATCcccccGATCcccccAATTcccccGATCcccccGATCcccccAATTcccccAATTcccccGATC
             ----     ----     ----     ----     ----     ----     ----     ----     ----     ----     ----     ---- 
AATT+GATC:               -------  -------  -------            ------  -------           -------           -------  
                            L1       L2        L3                L4      L5                L6                L7
  #of fragements with two enzyme recognization sites: 7
  Average length= sum(L1..L7)/7                         
===================================================================================
usage
===================================================================================
perl  GenomeCutter.pl Enzyme.list.txt genome.fasta -Min 2000 (the minimum length of contig used for enzyme cutting)
===================================================================================

